                </div></div></div></div><div class="Card FollowshipCard"><div class="NumberBoard FollowshipCard-counts NumberBoard--divider"><a type="button" class="Button NumberBoard-item Button--plain" href="/people/xing-zou-fan-xing/following"><div class="NumberBoard-itemInner"><div class="NumberBoard-itemName">关注了</div><strong class="NumberBoard-itemValue" title="83">83</strong></div></a><a type="button" class="Button NumberBoard-item Button--plain" href="/people/xing-zou-fan-xing/followers"><div class="NumberBoard-itemInner"><div class="NumberBoard-itemName">关注者</div><strong class="NumberBoard-itemValue" title="5">5</strong></div></a></div></div><div class="Profile-lightList"><a class="Profile-lightItem" target="_blank" href="/lives/users/7a8ad33d9c792d1ac0b10b2e41afb48b"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">赞助的 Live ⚡️</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">2</span></a><a class="Profile-lightItem" href="/people/xing-zou-fan-xing/following/topics"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">关注的话题</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">64</span></a><a class="Profile-lightItem" href="/people/xing-zou-fan-xing/following/columns"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">关注的专栏</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">128</span></a><a class="Profile-lightItem" href="/people/xing-zou-fan-xing/following/questions"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">关注的问题</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">29</span></a><a class="Profile-lightItem" href="/people/xing-zou-fan-xing/following/collections"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">关注的收藏夹</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">1</span></a></div></div></div></div></main></div></div><div id="data" style="display:none" data-state="{&quot;common&quot;:{&quot;ask&quot;:{}},&quot;privacy&quot;:{&quot;showPrivacy&quot;:false},&quot;loading&quot;:{&quot;global&quot;:{&quot;count&quot;:0},&quot;local&quot;:{&quot;people/get/&quot;:false,&quot;people/getActivities/xing-zou-fan-xing&quot;:false}},&quot;entities&quot;:{&quot;users&quo